<title>MORE LOVE TO THEE, OF CHRIST</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw, Krista hun hehpih-zawk diek ka nuom,
 Khupdin a ka pauchamna hih ngai in;
 Zie ka nget pen ahi, Krista hehpih zawk diek,
 Hehpih zaw diek Hehpih zaw diek.

[V2]
 2. Lei nawpna, muonna chawlh na ka na hawl,
 Tun Nang mai ka hun hawl ei pien-pha pen;
 Zie ka nget pen hina, Krista hehpih zawk diek,
 Hehpih zaw diek, Hehpih zaw diek.

[V3]
 3. Lungkham, lungzin leh nat na tuok mah leng,
 Nang sawl ahih chun kipakin pawm ka;
 La ei sakpih un tin, Krista hehpih zawk diek,
 Hehpih zaw diek, Hehpih zaw diek.

[V4]
 4. Ka hattawp pen inle, hun chawian ka,
 Ziechu ka lunggil khenna Aw hinna;
 Tihin paucham in a, Krista hehpih zawk diek,
 Hehpih zaw diek, Hehpih zaw diek.</lyrics>
</song>